            "text" : "The bug is annoying but since it doesn’t happen every time I don’t deem it necessary yet to go through the work of doing a full reset reinstalling and especially reconfiguring all app accounts. I have had this issue at least for the last 3 updates of tvOS. It is not going away and is shared among several apps. This points towards a common component that is used for streaming. This should be of interest to Apple as it will continue to occur possibly also with other users. This was working fine before and I did not do anything I can think of to affect such component, no reconfiguring tvOS or apps. This feels like a product bug.",
