            "urls" : [ ],
            "text" : "For the moment, let’s plan to redirect your concerns and questions to Phone Support. We see the depth of this concern and very much know that Apple Phone Support is in a better position, with more tool to really flush out what they can answer and resolve for you, and what may need to be addressed in another way. \n\nWe are glad to see you were able to get some resolution with your previous concerns, but others seem to still have questions marks with them and that’s where Phone Support will want to list and research your prior Case Notes. \n\nYou can reach phone support in Belgium at 0800 80 404 (French) or 0800 80 407 (Flemish). Our lines are open Monday through Friday from 8 a.m. to 7:45 p.m., and Saturday and Sunday from 10 a.m. to 5:45 p.m.\n\nIf you have problems calling through, please let us know and we can look for an alternative option to consider.",
