            "text" : "FYI here’s another occurrence of similar but this time spell check in MS Word on MacOS. how can the same spell check issue happen across devices, OS’s, software and hardware vendors? This needs urgent attention before it is deployed to take more people, organizations, and whole countries hostage. Wouldn’t you want to know what, who, why, since when, who sanctioned it?",
